title: John Berry - Standing on the Edge
description:
One of the greatest singers in country music is noted for the intense passion he has brought to such hits as "Standing on the Edge of Goodbye," "I Think About it All the Time" and "If I Had Any Pride Left at All", which  were all major hits in 1995.
